<h1><%= @user.username %>'s Player Profile</h1>

<%= link_to "Add a New Game", new_user_game_path(@user), :class => "btn btn-primary" %>

<h3>Your Stats:</h3>

<p><strong>High Score for One-on-One Game: </strong><%= @user.high_score_single_score %> volleys with Player <%= @user.high_score_single_partner %></p><br>

<p><strong>High Score for Group Game: </strong><%= @user.high_score_group_score %> volleys with Players <%= @user.high_score_group_partners %></p><br>

<p><strong>Number of Games: </strong><%= @user.games.count %></p><br>

<p><strong>Favorite Partner: </strong><%= @user.frequent_partner_name %></p><br>

<p><strong>Favorite Location: </strong><%= @user.frequent_location_name %></p><br>
